post_content: The Portofino Collection is a plain linen look sheer with a background with a leafy print. Lead weighted base, and wide width. This is best selling sheer has great colour selections to choose from. FR Rated so is suitable for both residental and commerical.

post_content: The Provence Collection is a floral embroidery, on a linen-look sheer fabric. The wide of this fabric is 320cm with a Lead-Weight. This fabric is FR Rated and so is suitable for both residential and commerical use. Provence is available in 4 on-trend shades
